<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Search - XSS Demo</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .warning {
      background: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #856404;
    }
    .search-box {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    input[type="text"] {
      width: calc(100% - 100px);
      padding: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px 0 0 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    button {
      width: 100px;
      padding: 12px;
      background: #f5576c;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s;
      display: inline-block;
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    button:hover {
      background: #e4465b;
    }
    .results {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      min-height: 100px;
    }
    .results h2 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .result-text {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .links {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .links a {
      color: #f5576c;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .links a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .demo-info {
      background: #ffe7e7;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-left: 4px solid #f5576c;
    }
    .demo-info h3 {
      color: #d32f2f;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .demo-info code {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-family: monospace;
      color: #d32f2f;
      display: block;
      margin: 5px 0;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .demo-info p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Search Page</h1>
    <div class="warning">
      <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Warning:</strong> Halaman ini sengaja vulnerable untuk demo XSS!
    </div>

    <form action="/search" method="GET" class="search-box">
      <input type="text" name="q" placeholder="Masukkan kata pencarian..." value="<%= searchQuery %>">
      <button type="submit">Cari</button>
    </form>

    <% if (searchQuery) { %>
      <div class="results">
        <h2>Hasil Pencarian:</h2>
        <div class="result-text">
          Anda mencari: <%= searchQuery %>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="demo-info">
      <h3>üö® XSS (Cross-Site Scripting) Demo:</h3>
      <p>Coba masukkan salah satu payload berikut di search box:</p>
      <code>&lt;script&gt;alert('XSS')&lt;/script&gt;</code>
      <code>&lt;img src=x onerror="alert('XSS')"&gt;</code>
      <code>&lt;svg onload="alert('XSS')"&gt;</code>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px;">Atau langsung akses URL:</p>
      <code>/search?q=&lt;script&gt;alert('XSS')&lt;/script&gt;</code>
    </div>

    <div class="links">
      <a href="/">‚Üê Kembali ke Home</a> |
      <a href="/login">Ke Login Page ‚Üí</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
